				<div class="accordion-item text-lg leading-relaxed">
					<button 
						class="accordion-trigger flex gap-2 items-start text-left" 
						aria-expanded="false"
						aria-controls="service-4">
						<div class="space-y-0.5">
							<div class="font-bold tracking-wide">5. Grant Writing & Technical Planning Support</div>
							<div>
								I help you scope technical work packages, write methodological and technical narratives, 
